    <chapter title="Run Testbrain CLI in your CI/CD pipeline or locally" id="about-testbrain-cli-run" >
        <p>Testbrain not provides native solutions for Azure Pipelines, CircleCI, GitHub, and TeamCity.
            But for CI/CD systems, you can use Testbrain CLI from PyPi package or Docker images.
